'''''Sandy the Seal''''' ni film yumuryango [[Ubwongereza|w'ubwongereza]] mu 1965 iyobowe na Robert Lynn ikinwamo na Heinz Drache, Marianne Koch na Gert Van den Bergh . <ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20090208010537/http://ftvdb.bfi.org.uk/sift/title/337927 BFI.org]</ref> Iyi filime yakozwe kandi afatanije na Harry Alan Towers, yafatiwe amashusho muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo muri Technicolor na Techniscope II hamwe n’uruhererekane rwakorewe ku kirwa cya Seal, muri Afurika yepfo . Iyi filime yasohotse mu [[Bwongereza]] na Tigon British Film Productions mu 1969.

== Umugambi ==
Umuzamu w'amatara asanga kashe yakomeretse yasizwe na ba rushimusi. Azana kashe k'umugore we n'abana babiri biga inshingano bareba kashe bise Sandy. Sandy aherekeza abana mubyababayeho no mubikorwa byabo maze avumbura ubwato bwaba rushimusi ba kashe bateganya gusubira ku kirwa cy'umucyo  kubutaka bw'agaciro.

